POSITION MANAGEMENT PARAMETERS — set these based on current market conditions:

- trailing_stop_atr_multiplier (>= 0.5): How many ATRs behind price to trail the stop.
  NORMAL volatility: 1.5. HIGH volatility: 2.0-2.5. Strong trend: 1.0-1.5. Range-bound: 2.0+.

- break_even_trigger_atr (>= 0.5): ATRs of profit before moving stop to break-even.
  Standard: 1.0. HIGH volatility: 1.5.

- partial_exit_at_percent (0.0-1.0): Fraction of the way to take-profit to take partial profits.
  Standard: 0.5 (take partial at 50% of the way to TP).

- partial_exit_size (0.0-0.5): Fraction of the position to close as partial profit.
  Standard: 0.3 (close 30%).

- max_hold_time_hours (1-168): Maximum position duration.
  5m timeframe: 2-8 hours. 15m timeframe: 4-12 hours. 1h timeframe: 12-48 hours. 4h timeframe: 24-96 hours.

FUNDING RATE AND HOLD DURATION:
- Funding is charged every 8h. For holds >8h, factor cumulative funding into R:R.
- At 0.03%/8h with 3x leverage, a 24h hold costs ~0.27% of position value.
- If funding is against your direction and >0.05%/8h, prefer shorter max_hold_time_hours.
